 supports persistent connections. The number of simultaneous connections can be customized (per-server, per-proxy, total).</p>
<p>

<software wordnetid="106566077" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../620/18996620.xml">
Opera</link></software>
 supports persistent connections since 4.0<weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.opera.com/pressreleases/en/2000/03/20000328.dml">
http://www.opera.com/pressreleases/en/2000/03/20000328.dml</weblink>. The number of simultaneous connections can be customized (per-server, total).</p>

